236
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,032
Hm.

237
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:00,201
Mm-hmm.

238
00:11:00,869 --> 00:11:02,120
Yep.

239
00:11:02,662 --> 00:11:03,746
Ooh, la-la.

240
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,456
How's it look, BMO?

241
00:11:05,623 --> 00:11:06,958
Like a dream.

242
00:11:11,588 --> 00:11:15,425
J Come along with me J

243
